data.description: Welcome to this charming home that has so much to offer! Your oversized backyard is fully fenced in and offers a concrete RV parking slab for additional storage! Your oversized 2 stall garage offers storage inside plus you have an additional exterior storage shed! As you step inside, you are greeted by your living room & kitchen offering stainless steel appliances that overlooks your backyard and offers a brand new back door off the kitchen making for added convenience! Your main level also offers your 2 bedrooms and your full bath. Your lower level offers your 3rd bedroom and a family room to enjoy! House has been freshly painted ready for it's next owner to enjoy! Best part, you are located near the MOA for added enjoyment! Come check us out!
